# CloudCore_Sync_2 CLI Documentation

## Overview

**CloudCore_Sync_2** is a production-grade, modular cybersecurity framework designed for enterprise deployment. The framework provides a plugin-based sync pipeline with CRDT-based conflict resolution, offline-first synchronization, and encrypted peer discovery.

